{"tid":456103,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"將性愛界限拿捏到位的Calvin Klein首本書曝光","createTime":"2017-11-02T16:19:41.000Z","updateTime":"2017-11-02T16:19:41.000Z","uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"1cdda6cf2364332d6e9f23c4bdf47e9a2d1b9993","tid":456103,"uid":14730,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-02T16:19:42.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/03/001849_d2bf0cbc3fbbde6fb4aa2ff3cfbd8288.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F03%2F001849_d2bf0cbc3fbbde6fb4aa2ff3cfbd8288.jpg&h=d41de81f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n除非大家都一同卸下有關Weinstein、Richardson的有色眼鏡，否則要討論有關性與時裝、模特兒、廣告之間等等的界限之話題，今天都變得困難。可是，豐厚的歷史告訴我們性這回事，卻一直存在時裝中，更成為時尚行銷、市場多年的基本工具。<br />\n <br />\n從來沒有一個人將性這回事拿捏得比Calvin Klein準確到位，在資訊科技尚未發達之時他已洞悉先機，以富驚人的挑釁意味之影像打造成今天的國際品牌，建立屬於品牌的深刻印象。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n圖：<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2z8zf60\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2z8zf60&d=NcqQRCZ2A5PjWhcJ3PxkfjCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=0e1f8b68\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2z8zf60</a>"}]}